                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41518",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It is not possible to add tagging because when a cache does not support tagging an notice\/warning is thrown.\r\n\r\nAs long as Zend_Cache does not support tagging, or a proper handling for un-tagable cache adapters, it is not possible for the I18n core to support tagging.\r\n\r\nTags have been erased 3 releases before as there were problems with this approach.\r\n\r\nNow, when using cache, Zend_Translate must have it's own cache or you omit using clearCache().",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-07-16T10:06:34.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-07-16T10:06:34.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41519",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=freak",
                        "name": "freak",
                        "displayName": "Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thomas you can use getCapabilities() to determine whether the cache returns tags. If it does; it should use tags rather than clearing it all - imho.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=freak",
                        "name": "freak",
                        "displayName": "Dolf Schimmel (Freeaqingme)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-07-16T10:32:52.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-07-16T10:32:52.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41522",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "There is no need to duplicate things which we already discussed and clearified.\r\n\r\nYou should give me some minutes to add a feature even if it's bug hunt day and I decleared that it works different that you noted within irc :-)",
